text: "How Deep Is Your Love" is a 2015 song by Scottish DJ Calvin Harris and English production trio Disciples. It features uncredited vocals by Norwegian singer and songwriter Ina Wroldsen. It topped the single charts in Australia, Belgium, Greece, Israel, Lebanon, Mexico, Romania and Russia and went to the top 5 in Austria, the Czech Republic, Denmark, Finland, France, Germany, Ireland, the Netherlands, New Zealand, Poland, Slovakia, South Africa, Switzerland and the United Kingdom. It also peaked at number 16 in Canada and number 27 in the United States. The music video features American model Gigi Hadid. == Track listing == == References == Category:2015 songs Category:Calvin Harris songs
